casebody.data:
Frank Javier NUNEZ, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1535 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 27, 2018 EMAS, LOGUE and LUCK, JJ., concur.

Upon consideration, petitioner's request for oral argument is denied.

Following review of the petition for writ of prohibition, and the response and reply thereto, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
